OL,3,CReform UK councillor suspended after
OL,4,Callegations she shared racist posts
OL,6,FA Reform UK councillor in
OL,7,FStaffordshire has been suspended by
OL,8,Fthe party after allegations she shared
OL,9,Fracist social media posts.
OL,11,FThe claims, published by campaign
OL,12,Fgroup Hope Not Hate, allege that posts
OL,13,Flinked to Lynn Dean include racist and
OL,14,Fdiscriminatory content.
OL,16,FAmong the posts highlighted, the
OL,17,Forganisation says she questions the
OL,18,Fintelligence of African people and
OL,19,Fnegatively commented on black people
OL,20,Fin a generalising statement.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
