OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1774768381
OL,3,CReform UK councillor suspended after
OL,4,Callegations she shared racist posts
OL,6,FThe councillor represents May Bank &
OL,7,FWolstanton in Newcastle-under-Lyme.
OL,8,FShe also sits on Newcastle-under-Lyme
OL,9,FBorough Council.
OL,11,FReform UK has confirmed Cllr Dean has
OL,12,Fbeen suspended pending an
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,FHope Not Hate said screenshots show
OL,16,Fposts allegedly shared by Cllr Dean
OL,17,Fcontaining derogatory comments about
OL,18,FBlack people, Muslims and other
OL,19,Fgroups. Some posts date back to 2018.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
