OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1774768381
OL,3,CReform UK councillor suspended after
OL,4,Callegations she shared racist posts
OL,6,FCllr Dean has been approached for
OL,7,Fcomment.
OL,9,FHope Not Hate argues the case forms
OL,10,Fpart of a wider pattern, pointing to
OL,11,Fprevious controversies involving
OL,12,FReform UK councillors in Staffordshire.
OL,14,FThese include the resignation of
OL,15,Fformer council leader Ian Cooper in
OL,16,FDecember following separate
OL,17,Fallegations of racist social media
OL,18,Factivity, as well as other
OL,19,Finvestigations involving councillors
OL,20,Fin the county.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
