OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1774768381
OL,3,CReform UK councillor suspended after
OL,4,Callegations she shared racist posts
OL,6,FThe organisation has raised concerns
OL,7,Fabout vetting and oversight within
OL,8,FReform UK at a local level.
OL,10,FMartin Murray, leader of Staffordshire
OL,11,FCounty Council, said: "I can confirm
OL,12,FCllr Dean has had the whip suspended
OL,13,Fbecause of unacceptable comments made
OL,14,Fon an anonymous account which was not
OL,15,Fdisclosed during vetting.
OL,17,F"Cllr Dean has now been suspended from
OL,18,FReform UK."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
