OL,3,CReform UK councillor suspended after
OL,4,Callegations she shared racist posts
OL,6,FA Reform UK spokesman said: "Upon
OL,7,Freview, it was found that Cllr Dean
OL,8,Fhad failed to declare her social media
OL,9,Faccount, operating under a different
OL,10,Fname, during our vetting process. Cllr
OL,11,FDean has had her membership of Reform
OL,12,FUK suspended pending investigation."
OL,14,FA Staffordshire County Council
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "We have been made
OL,16,Faware of allegations about comments on
OL,17,Fsocial media.
